{
  "stem": "3964.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "But in '33, things really started to get bad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "There wasn't a day I wasn't picked on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "There wasn't a day that one or another child would call me dirty Jew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "There wasn't a day that one or another child would pick on me, hit me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And things became progressively worse.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "In 1934, 1935, things were so bad that I couldn't even go home by myself anymore from school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "My mother had to pick me up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And even with my mother presence, at times, children would, would beat me up and call me names.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Things became very difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "In 1934, because of the problems we had in the German schools and also of a program, I suppose, which the Nazis initiated, we Jewish children-- there were five or six of us in the school-- were expelled from the school.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And a, quote, 'Jewish school' was opened with a teacher, who actually was not a teacher, but it was our chazan.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "It was the, the man who would sing and perform the, the prayers in synagogue, or lead the prayers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We did not have a lot rabbi.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "In 1936-- and, and that school was open in '34, I believe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And it went on till 1936.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "In 1936, all funds from the German government were taken away from the Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And the school was closed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "From 1936 to 1937, I was at home and not in any school at all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents, of course, were very protective of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my father, having been a extreme optimist all his life, always felt that this situation and condition wouldn't go on for very long.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Situation was a temporary situation and that Hitler would very soon be kicked out of the government.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And things would change for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
